This add-on allows you to had more features to cloze deletion. To gain a finer control to what you see in each card. A more detailled explanation is given on the page of the add-on for <a href="https://ankiweb.net/shared/info/873439973">version 2.0 </a>.

To report bug, and for more informations, please go to https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-enhanced-cloze

